OL,3,CMan who attacked wife with boot jack
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FA woman who was attacked with an iron
OL,7,Fboot jack by her violent husband said
OL,8,Fshe thought she was going to die.
OL,10,FJames Blundell, 54, used the implement
OL,11,F- a tool for removing footwear - to
OL,12,Fbludgeon wife Carleen after an
OL,13,Fargument at their home in
OL,14,FGoldsborough, near Knaresborough,
OL,15,FNorth Yorkshire, in November 2024.
OL,17,FWhen police found her she was covered
OL,18,Fin blood.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
