FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772020976
OL,3,CMan who attacked wife with boot jack
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FAfter Blundell was jailed for 30
OL,7,Fmonths, Mrs Blundell said the incident
OL,8,Fhad affected her "in many ways".
OL,10,FShe said in a statement: "I had got
OL,11,Fused to my husband's rages and violent
OL,12,Fepisodes over the years, but this was
OL,13,Fthe worst it had ever been.
OL,15,F"I thought I was going to die. It was
OL,16,Fthe first time I had felt that way. I
OL,17,Ffelt powerless."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
