FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772020976
OL,3,CMan who attacked wife with boot jack
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FYork Crown Court heard Blundell struck
OL,7,Fhis wife in the face and head, leaving
OL,8,Fher with serious injuries, including a
OL,9,Ftorn cartilage in her knee.
OL,11,FHe then dialled 999 from their home,
OL,12,Ftelling the call handler: "It's my
OL,13,Fwife, we've had an argument, we had a
OL,14,Ffight, I've hurt her,. It's my fault,
OL,15,Fshe's injured. We need the police and
OL,16,Fwe need an ambulance now."
OL,26,@tD@[OUxD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
