FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772020976
OL,3,CMan who attacked wife with boot jack
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FHe was arrested at the scene and told
OL,7,Fofficers: "There is no excuse for what
OL,8,FI have done. I've injured someone,
OL,9,Fpotentially fatally, who I have been
OL,10,Fwith for 28 years."
OL,12,FBlundell admitted wounding with
OL,13,Fintent. As well as the prison sentence
OL,14,Fhe was handed a five-year restraining
OL,15,Forder.
OL,17,FDet Con Abigail Garford, of North
OL,18,FYorkshire Police, said, "When I first
OL,19,Fmet Carleen, it was clear that she was
OL,20,Fstruggling both mentally and
OL,21,Fphysically after the attack.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@SO]zD@YOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
