OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772020976
OL,3,CMan who attacked wife with boot jack
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"She hadn't known life without her
OL,7,Fabuser for 28 years, and the prospect
OL,8,Fof rebuilding her life was
OL,9,Foverwhelming."
OL,11,FMrs Blundell said she now wants to
OL,12,Fhelp others escape abusive
OL,13,Frelationships.
OL,15,F"I am living a completely different
OL,16,Flife, and I see myself as a survivor,
OL,17,Fnot a victim," she said. "My aim now
OL,18,Fis to support others, and spread the
OL,19,Fword that there is light at the end of
OL,20,Fthe tunnel, and there are positive
OL,21,Foutcomes."
OL,26,@qD@NO]wD@AOU}D@JO]
